<h3> now it's video time</h3>

<video src="video.mp4"> if the video cant be played shows this text
</video>
<video src="video.mp4" controls> basic desc
the catch is without controls command you cannot play the video
</video>

<video src="video.mp4" controls width='500'> we have changed the width of the video hence it take cares of the height itself
</video>

<video src="video.mp4" poster="thumbnail.jpg" controls width='500'> we added the thumbnail to the video </video>

<video src="video.mp4" poster="thumbnail.jpg" loop controls width='500' autoplay> autoplay on  and loop on </video>

